EN: They plan to organize a marine conservation movement.

ZH: 鸟类在海洋边缘觅食。
EN: Birds forage at the edge of the ocean.

ZH: 这个海岛国家以其清澈的海洋而闻名。
EN: This island nation is famous for its pristine oceans.
